data.description: Wonderful opportunity for a ranch-style home with a finished walk-out lower level, backing to Lindbergh High School. This home has great potential with some TLC. Enter to find the living room with built-in bookcases and a wood-burning fireplace that opens to the dining room with French doors to the covered porch. Both the living room and dining room have wood flooring under the carpeting. The eat-in kitchen offers a gas cooktop, a built-in microwave, and views of the backyard. The primary bedroom has double closets and a full bath. 2 additional bedrooms and a full bath complete the main level. The walk-out lower level features a large rec room with built-ins, a family room with a fireplace, a wet bar area, a half bath, and ample space for storage. Additional features include main level laundry, 2 car rear entry garage, fenced yard, all brick exterior, and more!
